text.author: Mary Forester
text.title: I'm Pregnant! Early Pregnancy Vlog // First Trimester Weeks 4-12 | anothergirlslife
text.summary: After finding out she is pregnant, a vlogger who is now seven weeks pregnant and due in mid-September tells about her feelings, her decision to document her pregnancy on her vlog, her diet and cravings, getting doctor's and midwife appointments and experiencing nausea and headaches.
